                <p><strong>Gender:</strong> Male</p>
                <p><strong>Age:</strong> 2 years</p>
                <p><strong>Behaviour: </strong> Very friendly with everyone! </p>
                <p><strong>Description:</strong> Loyal and intelligent, enjoys companionship and is great with families. Loves long walks and playing with toys.</p>
                <button type="button">Interested</button>
